### REST Client Test File for VS Code REST Client Extension
### Install: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@accessToken = your_access_token_here
@projectId = project_id_here
@categoryId = category_id_here
@countryId = country_id_here

### Variables (set these after getting real values)
@userId = user_id_here
@submissionId = submission_id_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### Authentication Endpoints
### ============================================

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!@#",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!@#"
}

### Google OAuth (when implemented)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "google-id-token"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Cookie: refreshToken=your_refresh_token

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Cookie: refreshToken=your_refresh_token

### ============================================
### User Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update Current User
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### ============================================
### Metadata Endpoints (Public)
### ============================================

### Get Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### Get Countries
GET {{baseUrl}}/countries

### Get Tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/tags

### ============================================
### Project Endpoints (Public)
### ============================================

### List Projects (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects

### List Projects (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?page=1&limit=10

### List Projects (filtered by category)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?category=exchange

### List Projects (filtered by country)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?country=NG

### List Projects (filtered by tag)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?tag=lightning-network

### List Projects (search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?search=bitcoin

### List Featured Projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?featured=true

### Get Project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}

### ============================================
### Project Builder Endpoints (Authenticated)
### ============================================

### Create Project
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Bitcoin Project",
  "description": "A great Bitcoin project in Africa",
  "website": "https://example.com",
  "countryId": "{{countryId}}",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "city": "Lagos",
  "address": "123 Main Street"
}

### Update Project
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Project Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Submit Project for Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Please review this project"
}

### Delete Project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================
### Search Endpoint
### ============================================

### Search Projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=bitcoin

### Search with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=exchange&category=exchange&country=NG

### ============================================
### Review Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get Project Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/reviews

### Get Project Reviews (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/reviews?page=1&limit=10

### Create Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Great project!",
  "comment": "Really impressed with this service"
}

### ============================================
### Admin/Moderation Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get Submissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Submissions (filtered)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/submissions?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Approve Submission
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/submissions/{{submissionId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Reject Submission
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/submissions/{{submissionId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Project does not meet our guidelines"
}

### ============================================
### Analytics Endpoints
### ============================================

### Track Project View
POST {{baseUrl}}/analytics/view
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "referrer": "https://google.com"
}

### Track Project Click
POST {{baseUrl}}/analytics/click
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "url": "https://example.com"
}

